{"tid":2438850,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"1222萬買元朗合益廣場3房 衝上歷史新高價","createTime":"2021-03-08T21:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T15:38:27.000Z","uid":73269,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"772ee2c0dc29fafa09f799cbc4047fa51d03f252","tid":2438850,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T21:05:31.000Z","msg":"1222萬買元朗合益廣場3房 衝上歷史新高價<br />\n        <span class=\"x-large\">1222萬買元朗合益廣場3房 衝上歷史新高價</span><br />\n                <span class=\"xx-large\">1222萬買元朗合益廣場3房 衝上歷史新高價</span><br />\n<br />\n樓市氣氛持續向好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，刺激用家入市意慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，美聯物業元朗形點分行首席聯席區域經理陳鋒表示，元朗合益廣場錄得本月首宗成交，區內用家經該行購入高層3房套房單位，<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">火速獲區內用家洽商承接</span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，涉資1,222萬元。成交為合益廣場B座高層1室，實用面積844平方呎，3房套房連工人房間隔，享開揚市景。盡管屋苑樓齡逾二十年，惟單位內籠保持新淨，間隔實用，而且鄰近購物及交通配套完善，故受客人青睞，雙方議價後終以1,222萬元成交，實用呎價約14,479元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2005年5月以320萬元購入上述物業，是次轉手帳面大幅獲利902萬元，物業升值2.8倍。"},{"pid":"8e2c75c372d725d820c1a217bc1a2e9b28d52bbc","tid":2438850,"uid":19004,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T21:38:31.000Z","msg":"下面新街嘈撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34706576b2754bc841e01336b7711f4edb430861","tid":2438850,"uid":6604,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T21:41:07.000Z","msg":"街市嗰頭<br />\n條街勁污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60386bca2b1317fb0b2c4b18150b43c881321a0d","tid":2438850,"uid":179967,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T21:46:27.000Z","msg":"的確係幾完善 樓下就係街市 日鳩日嘈撚到"},{"pid":"718c6e04c2e45ab641a274f747a91b389cf82395","tid":2438850,"uid":213142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2